{"tid":560452,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賴恩美臣比卡希爾頂爆頭，宣佈掛靴","createTime":"2018-02-14T06:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T12:20:28.000Z","uid":4661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c4aeaccd7e1044eb263ad0413c979351ca5fab62","tid":560452,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518570268_ab30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518570268_ab30.jpg&h=3c26d630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518570269_5573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518570269_5573.jpg&h=a17c6acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n侯城中場賴恩美臣因為頭骨曾經骨裂，周二晚宣佈掛靴，年僅26歲就被逼結束球員生涯。在一次爭頂中導致賴恩美臣受傷的車路士後衛加利卡希爾坦言，他對事件發展至這個地步感到心碎。<br />\n<br />\n賴恩美臣是在去年1月一場與車路士的英超比賽當中，在一次角球爭頂當中，遭加利卡希爾頂中頭部導致骨裂。當時賴恩美臣要接受緊急手術，並住院一星期。這位現年26歲的中場今季原本希望復出，但因為醫生的建議，最終決定掛靴。車路士守將加利卡希爾得悉消息後，在個人Twitter撰文，「聽到消息簡直令我心碎，角球爭頂是我們做過不下千次的事，卻因此看到一名頂級的足球員落得如此下場，真的令人心碎......祝願他將來一切好運。」"},{"pid":"8786fb59b4f782f45404e76906dd5e703e8af0b7","tid":560452,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249e34d4999e8367ac579b35bca9032e31df1955","tid":560452,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"卡希爾唔跟埋掛靴？"},{"pid":"f660bef19087ba43debd9fe743d4f601c83022da","tid":560452,"uid":12660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"死車狗對住人 太陽穴頂"},{"pid":"8a889ae04df8e684422db6ce423f5e088d358286","tid":560452,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"頂撚死你"},{"pid":"5c6fd12931253c47d3145b79a3ab29169ab974a2","tid":560452,"uid":163405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"先廿六歲 就咁就退役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ae071e3ca3a36b102f35235d162c1692532fe7","tid":560452,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"249e34d4999e8367ac579b35bca9032e31df1955","tid":560452,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"卡希爾唔跟埋掛靴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"咁益轟迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}